{"tid":568874,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[HeHe] 互含生殖器,  超淫亂大學迎新照曝光","createTime":"2018-02-22T07:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T20:49:48.000Z","uid":44725,"like":44,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bfbe4a7dcf4d9fda71eb6633d8b233030fab9614","tid":568874,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/PaT6ZR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FPaT6ZR.gif&h=c74d7e49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紐卡斯爾大學爆發超淫亂迎新。<br />\n<br />\n2018-02-21 10:38 <br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕澳洲紐卡斯爾大學（University of Newcastle）爆出新生迎新染黃事件，甚至還有現場學生互含生殖器喝酒的影片，引起各界關注，校方對此事相當震驚，並強調會做出嚴厲處罰。 <br />\n<br />\n多段尺度大的影片和照片在網路上瘋傳，有學生含生殖器喝酒、新生被用酒淋生殖器、在宿舍走廊裸體的畫面，甚至還有新生的頭髮被剃光，被要求像狗一樣在地上用狗碗舔碗中的東西，這些影片都是大白天在公眾場所進行，且都有不少人圍觀。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/MlDrc0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FMlDrc0.gif&h=83320b5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名該校學生透露，每個新生都會被分配給一位學長，這些學長會對學弟做一些欺凌的事情，而且沒辦法反抗，不然就會被排擠，等到明年變成學長後，就可以用同樣的方法對待學弟，這是很病態的做法。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/GnB0CT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FGnB0CT.gif&h=f1fcc2d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紐卡斯爾大學發言人指出，會對這些不當的行為迅速採取行動，這些學生也會受到嚴厲的懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/t6Ghwb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Ft6Ghwb.gif&h=9ad3ce11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f299f918158d6a4efaf10989fec2b805acdb141a","tid":568874,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:59:59.000Z","msg":"gif more <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe40baaa3d77235c408d3e52743d3ef2a3bb7bf1","tid":568874,"uid":138658,"like":33,"dislike":